  "@type": "Organization",
  "name": "Universiti Kebangsaan Malaysia",
  "url": "https://www.ukm.my/portalukm/",
  "description": "Universiti Kebangsaan Malaysia (UKM), The National University of Malaysia, is a public research university in Bangi, Selangor. Its public, machine-readable developer footprint is concentrated in scholarly-communication infrastructure operated by the Perpustakaan Tun Seri Lanang (UKM Library), exposed via OAI-PMH 2.0 harvesting interfaces.",
